headline: Foundations for Duke Energy, Indiana Economic Development Association commit $150,000 to improve community access to affordable child care
summary: The Duke Energy Foundation and the Indiana Economic Development Association Foundation are committing $150,000 in grant funding to support organizations and projects focused on improving access to affordable child care in Indiana communities.
